ium":"drawing","CreditLine":"The Fitzwilliam Museum, Cambridge — Paintings, Drawings and Prints","URL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/id/object/7384","ImageURL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/imagestore/pdp/pdp38/3125.jpg"},{"ObjectID":74344,"Title":"","Artist":"Lowestoft Porcelain Manufactory","Date":"third quarter of 18th century","Medium":"soft-paste porcelain","CreditLine":"The Fitzwilliam Museum, Cambridge — Applied Arts","URL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/id/object/74344","ImageURL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/imagestore/aa/aa3/C_3042_1928_281_29.jpg"},{"ObjectID":75088,"Title":"","Artist":"Unknown","Date":"late 12th Century","Medium":"fritware (stonepaste)","CreditLine":"The Fitzwilliam Museum, Cambridge — Applied Arts","URL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/id/object/75088","ImageURL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/imagestore/aa/aa6/C_436_1991_281_29.jpg"},{"ObjectID":75832,"Title":"","Artist":"","Date":"","Medium":"lead-glazed earthenware","CreditLine":"The Fitzwilliam Museum, Cambridge — Applied Arts","URL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/id/object/75832","ImageURL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/imagestore/aa/aa3/C_690A_1928_281_29.jpg"},{"ObjectID":78064,"Title":"","Artist":"Waldher","Date":"Anglo-Norman","Medium":"coin","CreditLine":"The Fitzwilliam Museum, Cambridge — Coins and Medals","URL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/id/object/78064","ImageURL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/imagestore/cm/cm1/CM_1149_2001_281_29.jpg"},{"ObjectID":81784,"Title":"Plate: The Boar and the Wolf","Artist":"Battersea Enamel Manufactory","Date":"mid-18th Century","Medium":"stoneware","CreditLine":"The Fitzwilliam Museum, Cambridge — Applied Arts","URL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/id/object/81784","ImageURL":"https://data.fitzmuseum.cam.ac.uk/imagestore/aa/aa7/C_81_1992.jpg"},{"ObjectID":84016,"Title":"","Artist":"Rome","Date":"236–237","Medium":"coin","CreditLine":"The Fitzwilliam Museum, Cambridge — Coins and Medals","URL"